{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"革命的激情涌心头","authors":["王术"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的激情涌心头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花的城，红旗的海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命师生从八方来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日照天安门晴空万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庆祝毛泽东思想的新胜利。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千言万语说哪一句？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬爱的毛主席和我们在一起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着毛主席不想走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的激情涌心头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“万岁！万万岁！”高声呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决走毛主席指引的路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和人民心连心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼世界干革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥护党决定的十六条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎接文化大革命新高潮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全会公报是及时雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜得我们载歌又载舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的大船行万里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的舵手是毛主席。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世世代代听毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀山火海全不怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风大浪里举红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决把文化大革命进行到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国科学技术大学　王术"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}